<div id="landingPage">
  <img src="/assets/huskyOnBeach.jpg" class="img-responsive" id="backgroundImg" alt="dog on beach"/>
  <div id="howWeWork" class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-xs-4" id="whatissite">
      <h2 class="text-primary">What is eDoggy?</h2>
      <p class="text-primary">Ever in a situation where you need someone to come and walk your dog, fast? Now you can request a dog walker at a moments notice. The walker will come to you and walk your dog for 30 minutes. All walkers have a rating between 1-5 from other users, and dogs are rated on their aggression and confidence. eDoggy makes your life, and you best friend's life a little easier</li>
    </div>
    <img src="/assets/goldenSmile.jpg" alt="dog smiling" class="col-lg-4 col-xs-4 img-responsive img-circle" id="goldenSmile"/>
    <div id="howitworks" class="col-lg-4 col-xs-4">
      <h2 class="text-primary">How it Works</h2>
      <ol class="text-primary">
        <li>Sign in with your Facebook account</li>
        <li>Search for a dog walker via neighborhood or by their rating</li>
        <li>When you find one that you like click <span class="text-success">Schedule a walk</span></li>
        <li>The walker you choose will be notified via text message that they have a walk request</li>
        <li>When the walker accepts the walk appointment he / she will go to the designated meeting place and walk your dog for 30 minutes</li>
        <li>On confirmation of your dogs return pay the walker and up/down vote the walker</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <h2 class="headers col-lg-12 col-xs-12"> What users say about eDoggy...</h2>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-xs-4">
      <img src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/616029620312260608/TbsP2Ovj.jpg" class="img-circle col-lg-5 col-xs-5" />
      <p class="text-success">
        "eDoggy is great, when I needed a walker quickly I was able to find someone closeby to walk my dog. She was prompt, nice and my dog loved her! Will use this site again."
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-xs-4">
      <img src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/570630963555737600/09d-qHUt.jpeg" class="img-circle col-lg-5 col-xs-5" />
      <p class="text-success">
        "Being a dog walker on eDoggy allows me to pick up some extra money in the week, and I love meeting and spending time with all kinds of dogs in my neighborhood."
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-xs-4">
      <img src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/435878361735249920/y1-4jQna.png" class="img-circle col-lg-5 col-xs-5" />
      <p class="text-success">
        "I keep my dog with me at my business. I had a client coming in last minute that was afraid of dogs. With a few clicks I had someone to walk my dog while I was with my client."
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="signupLogin" class="col-lg-2 col-xs-2">
    <h2 class="headers">Get started!</h2>
    <% if current_user %>
      <a class="btn btn-success" href='/#/users/<%= current_user.id %>/edit'>Set up your profile</a>
    <% else %>
      <p class="headers">Sign up with facebook</p>
      <%= link_to "Facebook", "/auth/facebook", id: "sign_up", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
